Title: Einhell 49576105 3 Piece Professional Cordless Reciprocating Sabre Saw Blade Set
Description:
Designed for use with cordless reciprocating saws, this professional grade blade set includes a fine cut blade for wood, a rough cut blade for wood, and a bi metal blade for metal, plastic, and nail embedded wood.

These blades have an energy efficient design which helps to ensure longer runtimes with cordless machines. They are compatible with all Einhell reciprocating saws as well as all standard reciprocating saws from other manufacturers.
